<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Support</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: white;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
        }

        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .contact-info a {
            color: #ffcc00;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .contact-info a:hover {
            color: #ff9900;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Electricity Billing System Support</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the support page for our Electricity Billing System. We are here to help you with any questions or issues you may encounter while using our system.</p>
        <p>Our system is designed to provide a seamless and efficient way to manage your electricity bills. If you experience any difficulties or have any queries about your account, bill calculations, or payment options, please reach out to us.</p>
        <p>We are committed to ensuring that you have the best possible experience with our service. Our support team is available 24/7 to assist you with any problems you may face.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>For immediate assistance, contact us at:</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:support@electricitybilling.com">support@electricitybilling.com</a></p>
            <p>or call us at +91 86399 82518</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
